dct_description_sm: Map shows populated areas, native settlements, important buildings, churches, mosques, synagogues, embassies, schools, hospitals, roads, railways, tunnels, bridges, boundaries, powerlines, landmarks, vegetation, and water features. Includes guide to numbered features, index to streets, glossary, and location map. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Map information as of 1993." "WGS 84." "Grid--1,000 meter UTM zone 34." "Printed by NIMA." "This sheet falls within NK 34-5, 1501A 1:250,000 and 3280 III, M709, 1:50,000." "NSN 7643014033664." "NIMA Ref. No M903XPRISTINA." "Where street names cannot be shown on the graphic, the streets are identified by numbers."
dct_publisher_sm: [Bethesda, M.D.] : National Imagery and Mapping Agency, 1999.
